name: hinanawi tenshi touhou
description: 比那名居天子的lora。做了挺长时间的天子，但是裙子的彩虹块真的很难搞。站立状态目前还算稳定，坐下后由于裙子有褶皱，彩虹块就开始乱七八糟了，后续可能会再更新

modelVersions.name: v10.2.1
modelVersions.description:
中文：

优点：更好看，更稳定，站立状态下彩虹块还是很好看的

缺点：裙子边的彩虹块还是差强人意，搭配多个lora和controlnet可能还是会需要ps小小地修一下。

这次的升级还是一个触发词囊括人物特征和衣服特征，因此想给天子换衣服的诸位可能又失望了。

如果你在使用过程中遇到脸部崩坏和肢体畸形，也许是过拟合了，你可以先试着把权重调低一些；如果依然有问题，可以试着把分辨率调高，但有概率会出多人（一会儿我会放出黑历史，确实好看的，不忍心删掉就ps裁剪了一下）

translate：

Pros: It looks better, more stable, and the rainbow blocks are still pretty when she stand up.

Cons: The rainbow blocks on the edge of the skirt are still not very good, and I might need to do some minor editing with Photoshop if I want to combine multiple Lora and ControlNet models.

This update is still a trigger word that covers both the character’s features and the clothing features, so those who want to change tenshi’s clothes might be disappointed again. （sorry~）

If you encounter face collapse or limb deformation during use, it might be overfitting. You can try lowering the weight first; if there are still problems, you can try increasing the resolution, but there is a chance that it will generate multiple people (I will post some Incorrect result , they look really good, I couldn’t bear to delete them so I just cropped them a bit)
